{"tid":446403,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"換大電後，車cam熄匙後就無電...","createTime":"2017-10-24T09:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T03:36:38.000Z","uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9459503cdbff5ba3df6359526f32dae538a7bbd1","tid":446403,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T09:19:05.000Z","msg":"二手車入手無耐，一路無搞過車cam setting<br />\n原本熄匙後仲識錄4個鐘<br />\n<br />\n換大電後，一熄匙後就無電自己關機...<br />\n<br />\n係咪換電時師傅駁漏野??<br />\n<br />\n又可以點樣整番好??<br />\n<br />\n暫無圖..."},{"pid":"791d6d59b3f536b402afe8b2c8d4f484413ee853","tid":446403,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T23:33:52.000Z","msg":"小推.."},{"pid":"b8e2c58b7b509d7dea6a4e39ebfde4ca79378f1b","tid":446403,"uid":33908,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:28:54.000Z","msg":"換大電唔會攪到你啲線啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你部cam自己粒電死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b1535278b94f82629253167cbfe808a2b94f0f","tid":446403,"uid":43478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:43:23.000Z","msg":"換大電正路唔會搞到車cam線架喎"},{"pid":"84ab95811289d02ca14132acd4dcefbd717df04c","tid":446403,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:04:02.000Z","msg":"個cam係咪另外有條電線駁住個正極，換電時無駁返落去?"},{"pid":"f2bf835129eb0f09f447ed0a58efb84c1a13ae6f","tid":446403,"uid":137220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/110627_9a456249858278662758111c0b986871.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F110627_9a456249858278662758111c0b986871.jpg&h=ca455338&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/110629_522f35435ae466b4e769c0a2cb2dff30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F110629_522f35435ae466b4e769c0a2cb2dff30.jpg&h=db58fc98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3250ad1870e37402aacbc924867ae66912877b31","tid":446403,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:09:38.000Z","msg":"大電應該駁左???<br />\n<br />\n所以我估係車cam電問題...?<br />\n舊電寫住 3.7V 320mAh 303040<br />\n<br />\n邊度可以買到呢D電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b95ae2ae88bb8c0dfc0db423df73224bc2f222b","tid":446403,"uid":10460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:13:01.000Z","msg":"隻cam 有冇駁長火？冇駁長火的話，熄匙後要就會靠車cam本身既電繼續run，如果你每日著車幾個鐘，都仲有可能差返滿舊電，否則，冇咩時間差電，隻cam 又點會有電？"},{"pid":"556627650f98a3111b9d99d89b8d1c32dacd491e","tid":446403,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:36:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隻cam 有冇駁長火？冇駁長火的話，熄匙後要就會靠車cam本身既電繼續run，如果你每日著車幾個鐘，都仲有可能差返滿舊電，否則，冇咩時間差電，隻cam 又點會有電？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實唔知咩叫長火...<br />\n呢幾日keep住每日行兩三個鐘車<br />\n<br />\n但一熄匙，佢就即刻display無電...就自動熄機<br />\n<br />\n睇落應該真係舊內置電收左皮..?"}]}